{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I remember standing in one of the showers at the lousing-- delousing and my cousin I was with, he says to me, my god, look at yourself, just skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I says, you're telling me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Look at yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were so emaciated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were so skinny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We were just scared looking at one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "This was life in Blechhammer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "People were dying constantly, work was hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Some people traded their bread for cigarettes, but they went fast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was just impossible to-- people were stealing, one from or another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They were on their way, wherever somebody on the-- on the plant being with-- being with so many different nationalities, there was some haggling, some-- some bargaining, some dealing, wheeling and dealing going on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But there were so many-- so little food, so many people trying to grab whatever they could it was just impossible to survive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow, how we survived I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But worse than that, worse than the hunger pangs and all this here was the hopelessness, the treatment, the-- the degradation, dehumanization, the tortures, the anguish, the suffering.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember one night I said to my brother, we met at night, do you think we'll ever get out of here?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no hopes and expectations to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they took away our mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went numb.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We actually got numb, [? but yet ?] we had feelings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then another thing, every so often they had their hangings we had to witness.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This plant, this particular plant-- and I must touch on this here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This particular plant was very vital for the German war machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the English tried to bomb it, I mean to flatten it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They bombed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every so often, they bombed it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
